cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use P-SCA in academic work, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "P-SCA: Prompt Specification Curve Analysis"
abstract: "A toolkit for multiverse analysis of LLM prompt specifications. Implements Latin Hypercube sampling over researcher-controlled prompt dimensions, variance decomposition by dimension, Fisher r-to-z dominance tests, permutation inference, and specification curve plotting for LLM-based silicon-sampling studies."
